MongoDb ----- database hota h jahan data store hota h ksika bh --(whtasp, instagarm etc)--(jo apps ap banao ge unka data jahan store hota h usko khete hain database
tow types of database ---(relation ---mysql) ---(non-relational----mongodb)
mongodb ma data json formate ma hota h mtlb  k documents
mongodb --(mongodb k jo documents hote hain BSON ma store hote hain
model(code)------ collection
schema(code)--------documents (document ka data kese hoga
client ---- jo bh brower ho jis py hum internet chla sakhen (server se client ma save krwana hoto cookies)
----cookies

server --- py hota h section (data server py save krna ho tou section)
BSON ---- binary json  ---data type ko extend krne k lye data type ko banaya gaya--- json se BSON banaya gya
mongo compass----(apk local server se ksi bh server ko connect krna connect krna)---(apk system se ksi bh server ko connnect krna




